    Conditions: 
        * bass note goes down a semitone
        * [second interval] then down a tone
        * [third interval] then down a tone 
        * last note is on 1st beat
    Figures:
        * 1st note gets no figure
        * 2nd note gets a 6
        * 3rd note gets #6
        * 4th note gets no figure
