Rule x - 27 maybe
    K's rule:   21
    Page:       xx
    Conditions: 
        * When bass note goes down a tone
        * [second interval] then down a semitone
        * [third interval] then down a tone
        * [fourth interval] then down a tone
    Figures:
        * 1st note gets no figure
        * 2nd note gets a 6#42 or just ‘-‘
        * 3rd gets a 6
        * 4th gets a 6
        * 5th gets no figure
    Questions?
        * TBD!

