Rule x - 30 maybe
    K's rule:   24
    Page:       xx
    Conditions: 
        * When bass note goes up a tone, 
        * [second interval] then up a semitone, 
        * [third interval] then up a tone, 
        * [fourth interval] then up a tone
    Figures:
        * 1st note gets no figure
        * 2nd note gets a #6
        * 3rd note gets a 6
        * 4th note gets a 65
        * 5th note gets no figure
    Questions?
        * TBD!

Rule x - 31 maybe
    K's rule:   25
    Page:       xx
    Conditions: 
        * When at a cadence – -sol sol ut
    Figures:  
        * 1st note gets 4
        * 2nd note gets 7
        * 3rd note gets no figure
    Questions?
        * TBD!

Rule x - 32 maybe
    K's rule:   26
    Page:       xx
    Conditions: 
        * cadence – short sol ut
    Figures:
        * Short sol gets 7 (no 4) 
        * ut gets no figure
    Questions?
        * TBD!

Rule x - 33 maybe
    K's rule:   27
    Page:       xx
    Conditions: 
        * When at a cadence – long sol ut
    Figures:
        * Long sol gets 4 and 7
        * ut gets no figure
    Questions?
        * TBD!

Rule x - 34 maybe
    K's rule:   28
    Page:       xx
    Conditions: 
        * When at a cadence and sol is 3 beats in ¾ time
    Figures:
        * Sol gets 4, no figure, then a 7 (respectively on each beat)
    Questions?
        * TBD!